name: Algal community on the pneumatophores of mangrove trees of Gazi Bay in July and August 1987
description: Data on the location of found macroalgal and seagrass species and studyof the algal community on the pneumatophores of mangrove trees on the Westcoast of Gazi Bay during Julyand August 1987.
